# Plan Reference Requirement

- Before implementing, editing, debugging, or proposing architecture changes, read and reference `Plans/Plan.txt`.
- Treat `Plans/Plan.txt` as the primary source of product and system requirements.
- If a task appears to conflict with `Plans/Plan.txt`, pause and explicitly flag the conflict before proceeding.
- Keep all new logic aligned with modularity, security, and performance constraints defined in `Plans/Plan.txt`.
